STATE of North Carolina
v.
Dwayne Demont HAIZLIP No. 345P16-3 Supreme Court of North Carolina. April 13, 2017 James D. Concepcion, Assistant Attorney General, J. Douglas Henderson, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina. Dwayne Dumont Haizlip, for Haizlip, Dwayne Dumont.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Defendant on the 10th of April 2017 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Guilford County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 13th of April 2017."

Ervin, J. recused
